    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts its original factory finish, free of any swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-delivered' state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty liners, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of every service interval performed exclusively by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule specimen for the discerning collector who demands perfection. Viewing by appointment only to ensure the vehicle remains in its current pristine state.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
