    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally letting go of my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it waxed and garaged every single night. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
