      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This A80 Supra Turbo is a textbook example of JDM engineering excellence. The heart of this machine is the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, featuring its original sequential twin-turbocharger setup and factory intercooler. Power is delivered through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid, with no signs of oxidation on the subframes or suspension mounting points. The engine bay is immaculate, retaining all factory heat shielding and vacuum routing. The interior features the driver-centric cockpit with fully functional analog instrumentation and pristine upholstery. For the discerning collector seeking mechanical purity and a documented service history, this is an unmolested, investment-grade specimen.",
